{"tid":834212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：美國制裁中國軍方意在遲滯中國國防現代化","createTime":"2018-09-24T05:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T10:31:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5b082e61cbb1e35c6b66d75ed5ade25b6f33e3","tid":834212,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"《人民日報》發動評論文章指出，特朗普政府上台以來，美方抱守冷戰思維，將中國列為「戰略競爭者」，加大對華防範遏制。除對中國輸美產品加徵關稅外，美阻撓「中國製造2025」、制裁中興公司、將44家中國企業列入出口管制清單、出台《外國投資風險審查現代化法案》，此次更是劍指中國軍工裝備部門，可謂環環相扣、「一脈相承」，根本目的是打壓中國高新科技發展，遲滯中國國防現代化建設。中美關係發展歷程證明，中美合則兩利、鬥則俱傷。美國統治者要認識到，中國的發展是阻擋不了的。奉勸美方還是及早懸崖勒馬，不要再倒行逆施，早日回到理智、正確軌道上來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2167317/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%A8%E9%81%B2%E6%BB%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2167317%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%2581%25B2%25E6%25BB%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%258C%2596&d=TdIywUwWg4I4fsrcBNr70PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=378433d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2167317/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E6%84%8F%E5%9C%A8%E9%81%B2%E6%BB%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%A3%E5%8C%96</a>"},{"pid":"bedf05abfe7fc3a6bf2fda56a06711f4ebc7e55e","tid":834212,"uid":184679,"like":9,